n him, instructed me, \u201cDo not associate anything with Allah, even if you are slashed and burned. Do not leave the obligatory prayers on purpose, for whoever leaves them on purpose has forfeited the protection of Allah. Do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42315,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/11\/09\/spending-pairs\/","url_meta":{"origin":36456,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Spending pairs in the way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019sa\u2019ah ibn Mu\u2019awiyah reported: I met Abu Dharr, may Allah be pleased with him, and I said, \u201cNarrate a saying to me.\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cYes. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said: No Muslim servant spends a pair of any kind of wealth in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14543,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/03\/abu-musa-humble-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36456,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Burial: Abu Musa&#8217;s request for a humble funeral, burial","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: Abu Musa al-Ashari, may Allah be pleased with him, instructed us at the time of his death, saying, \u201cYou should hasten with my funeral procession. Do not follow me in suspense, do not put anything in my grave that will come between me and the dust, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/dua-new-convert-revert\/","url_meta":{"origin":36456,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for a new convert to Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Tariq ibn al-Ashyam reported: Whenever a man embraced Islam, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would teach him the prayer. Then, the Prophet instructed him to supplicate with these words, \u201cO Allah, forgive me, have mercy on me, guide me, grant me wellness, and provide for me.\" The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/07\/luqman-life-heart-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":36456,"position":5},"title":"Luqman on Life: Knowledge gives life to hearts, like rain on earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik reported: Luqman al-Hakim, upon him be peace, instructed his son, saying, \u201cO my son, sit with the scholars and keep close to them. Allah gives life to the hearts with the light of wisdom, just as he gives life to the dead earth with rain from the sky.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\